sentences.sentence: The May 4 sample (far left), collected by the Dauphin Island Sea Lab, Ala.
sentences.translation: 最左方的瓶子里是阿拉巴马州多芬岛海洋实验室5月4日采集的样品。

sentences.sentence: Like the rest of his fellow residents of Dauphin County, Mike Pintek had no answers.
sentences.translation: 但和其他生活在多芬郡的居民一样，麦克·平塔克也没有答案。

sentences.sentence: No one at the Dauphin County Civil Defense office knew what was going on. Pintek then decided to call Three Mile Island.
sentences.translation: 但是多芬郡国民防卫办公室的人不知道发生了什么，于是平塔克决定打电话给三哩岛(Three Mile Island)。
